data.description: ACCEPTED OFFER.  MULTIPLE OFFERS!  HIGHEST AND BEST MUST BE IN BY NOON MONDAY, FEBRUARY 26TH.  Beautifully updated home nestled on a serene wooded lot. This charming FOUR bedroom, two bath home offers the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility. A picturesque landscape welcomes you with towering trees and lovely landscaping.  The two car detached garage provides ample parking plus abundant storage space. The expansive backyard provides a lovely family sized deck offering endless opportuities for outdoor enjoyment, whether it's gardening, entertaining friends and family or simply enjoying the beauty of nature.   Come check this lovely home  with the perfect combination of comfort, convenience and natural beauty.
